{"tid":644963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(今次謝安琪點睇?)11歲女童甲流併發敗血病持續腦癎　此前已接種本季疫苗","createTime":"2018-04-27T16:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T17:09:32.000Z","uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ced871f21ffa5250478073822ee5f1163cb4b462","tid":644963,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"衛生署衛生防護中心周五（27日）晚公布，一名11歲有長期病患女童，周四（26日）起出現發燒、咳嗽帶痰、流鼻水和身體抽搐等病徵，送到瑪嘉烈醫院急症室後，再轉到深切治療部。其鼻咽分泌樣本經化驗後，證實對甲型流感病毒呈陽性反應，臨牀診斷為甲型流感併發敗血病和持續腦癇狀態，現時情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n中心初步調查顯示，發病女童已接種今季季節性流感疫苗，潛伏期內沒有外遊，其家居接觸者至今沒有病徵。<br />\n<br />\n中心正調查該女童所就讀的青衣一所學校，近日爆發的上呼吸道感染個案。包括該女童在內，共一男四女年介8至16歲學童和一名男職員，周二（24日）起出現發燒、咳嗽、流鼻水和喉嚨痛等上呼吸道感染病徵。除上述個案外，一名學生和該名男職員亦曾經求醫，兩人無需入院。除了該女童的個案外，其他病人現時情況<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180427/s00001/1524844574413?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180427%2Fs00001%2F1524844574413%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=CeQB9ayxr9xG%2F5Jj959dQBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=520b58f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180427%2Fs00001%2F1524844574413%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=d9ec9948\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180427/s00001/1524844574413?web_push=1</a><br />\n甲型好似真係得1成有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d87b2a402536a7e4557dbd71cf0111b2aaea00","tid":644963,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛賈雨村抹黑本土派有功<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132845_ea3dc39ca0