url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518336041499&d=CeQB9ayxr9xG%2F5Jj959dQBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=11e6b717\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518336041499&h=9f8f4dcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518336041499</a><br />\n<br />\n隻疫苗如果得一成效果你打唔打呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:44:14.000Z","msg":"打<br />\n<br />\n有一成機會唔洗仆街點解唔打？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你條友病撚咗唔好用香港啲醫療福利 番上人民醫院吊成世鹽水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"358fa1101a475f9eaca62960cc0e1c0c78a79d4d","tid":644963,"uid":34444,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 袁國勇又強調，疫苗非常安全，副作用發生機會只有百萬分之二至三，但保護率通常達四成至七成。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n信者得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a9adfad0604cabe00a25bf4a6520dc8e1e4eba","tid":644963,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"358fa1101a475f9eaca62960cc0e1c0c78a79d4d","tid":644963,"uid":34444,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 袁國勇又強調，疫苗非常安全，副作用發生機會只有百萬分之二至三，但保護率通常達四成至七成。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n信者得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"用番你既理論<br />\n有機會中副作用,做乜要打?<br />\n唔好話一成唔仆街多過百萬分之X多咁多呀<br />\n中唔中本身就係百分之50機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係講6成有效既乙型呀,我講緊得1成既甲型咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_news%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588%2F&d=CeQB9ayxr9xG%2F5Jj959dQBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c9a5cd5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有指本港疫苗未能有效抵抗H3甲型流感，周鎮邦承認，根據澳洲數據，現疫苗對H3流感僅得10%效用，但強調「都係有作用」。另他指出，政府將考慮引入南半球疫苗，但須預先與藥廠商量</span>。"},{"pid":"55813f4986c58a22ce54f0ba9975b59353c5034a","tid":644963,"uid":57700,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"399e219193291668269b7a0bd1810f42b8fe7352","tid":644963,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db291527171659560952073d9d7baa316e8016cb","tid":644963,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3662d7ecdf6d2a48aac76a0c752c6c8a8be4f6a5","tid":644963,"uid":34444,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99d87b2a402536a7e4557dbd71cf0111b2aaea00","tid":644963,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛賈雨村抹黑本土派有功<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=211da708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice